{{notability|Sport|date=May 2012}}
The '''Perth Glory End of Season Awards''' are the individual awards won by players of the [[Australia]]n [[Association Football|football]] club, [[Perth Glory]], who compete in each of the [[A-League]], [[A-League National Youth League|National Youth League]] and [[W-League (Australia)|W-League]] competitions. These awards are presented annually at the clubs' presentation night following the completion of the A-League season.
